message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and expectations. Given its exceptional quality and features, it's valued at $12000 to you. Considering its worth and the value it would bring to you, I am offering it to you for $10000. This is an opportunity to acquire a high-quality item at a competitive price. If you're interested, please let me know so we can proceed with the transaction.
